  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Zermatt</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/7b472ab866b14527be25caad79fb5068" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7b472ab866b14527be25caad79fb5068}" title="Le Mirabeau Hotel &amp; Spa">Le Mirabeau Hotel &amp; Spa</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13104685/le-mirabeau-garten-_-haupthaus.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/ed440d94eb384a25ae913d75e3711b96" /></p>
<p>Guests return year after year to the Mirabeau for is elegant style and friendly atmosphere. The Alpine Hideaway Spa is the perfect spot for a relaxing afternoon, or if the weather's good grab a sun loungers in the garden.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/8fa1210d0a794f8597980dec5856b80f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8fa1210d0a794f8597980dec5856b80f}" title="Hotel Alex">Hotel Alex</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13104686/wellness_whirlpool-030-lowres.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/94a8255dc66943a48a2ab979b1550ef6" /></p>
<p>The Hotel Alex has grand décor and a great location close to the train station and Gornergrat mountain railway. After a day of exploring, you'll return to fantastic wellness facilities and impeccable service from the friendly team. </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">View All Hotels in Zermatt</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></facilityDescription>
  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Lucerne</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/e8f256d55487463f84eb2747682db532" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8f256d55487463f84eb2747682db532}" title="Montana Art Deco Hotel">Montana Art Deco Hotel</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13109607/hotel_montana_lucerne_exterior.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7b37628edbf94025a85fd580abf4413e" />This stylish hotel has a hillside location overlooking Lake Lucerne, with fantastic views. Relax on the Beach Club Terrace, or eat in the award-winning restaurant. Access to the lakefront is easy thanks to the private elevator and the city centre is a short walk away.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef}" title="Lucerne" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View All Hotels in Lucerne</a></p>
<h2>Hotels in Weggis</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/55c38eb58134499d9afd758935f50cdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/55c38eb58134499d9afd758935f50cdf}" title="Hotel Alexander">Hotel Alexander</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13109609/hotel_alexander_weggis_swimming_pool.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/8135869f38114e7b8302ff01a510f06d" />This small and friendly hotel is located close to the lake shore on the outskirts of the pretty town of Weggis. The spa and gardens are the perfect place for a relaxing afternoon, with panoramic views over the lake and fantastic facilities.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/7ab6cce94c7d403ca2d33babf798ddb3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7ab6cce94c7d403ca2d33babf798ddb3}" title="Hotel Gerbi">Hotel Gerbi</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13109608/hotel_gerbi_weggis_exterior.jpg?width=320&amp;height=220" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/f76851c9f87d4133818bfae748ef6ef3" />The Hotel Gerbi shares facilities with the neighbouring Hotel Alexander, so also benefits from great wellness facilities and picturesque lake views. With only 25 rooms, it's a cosy and welcoming hotel.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e67e0510aeab481fa844cb74e63612a6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e67e0510aeab481fa844cb74e63612a6}" title="Weggis" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View All Hotels in Weggis</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></familyDescription>
